data.description: Welcome home to Townhome luxury in the must sought after neighborhood of Belmont Hills. This gorgeously kept 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom is just what the Doctor ordered for your next move. A combination of hard wood floors and above average carpets give 2295 Rolling Trails a pop of luxury, while injecting Suttle hints of style. The doses of white and grey throughout the home entice you into main living room, kitchen Open floor plan. The unique fireplace design and location, provide the best place for the big screen TV.  The kitchens all black, metallic appliances provide just the right space for eating/entertaining with family & friends. Recessed lighting, custom fans and modern bookcases round out the first floor high lights.      Heading up to the second, the oversized master bedroom includes a cute seating area and large closet space. The master bath houses a huge garden tub and stand up shower combo. The additional 2 bedrooms are a comfortable size with large closets. With a nice sized backyard, you will definitely be excited to came this hidden gem home. A motivated seller means: This can be yours if "The Price is Right"!
